<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ف ق أ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٨١٠ - ف ق أ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تفقَّأَ يتفقَّأ، تَفَقُّؤًا، فهو مُتَفَقِّئ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• تفقَّأت السَّحابةُ:</span> تبعجت عن مائها.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• تفقَّأ الدُّمَّلُ:</span> تشقَّق وخرج ما فيه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• تفقَّأ الرَّجلُ شحمًا:</span> امتلأ شحمًا حتى تشقق جلدُه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>